dct_description_sm: Oriented with north toward right. "21" in lower right corner. "Entered according to act of Congress in the year 1860 by S. Augustus Mitchell, Jr. in the Clerk's Office of the District Court for the Eastern District of Pennsylvania"--Recto, below border. Map surrounded by decorative border. Shows wards, railroads, public buildings, etc.
